{"tid":174613,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"警方落案起訴佔中三子、陳淑莊、邵家臻、學聯前常委等多人涉公眾妨擾罪","createTime":"2017-03-27T02:54:19.000Z","updateTime":"2017-03-27T03:18:11.000Z","uid":28366,"like":1,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"a2ba83e6498335f41974f4e59d7a7faaf99e4522","tid":174613,"uid":28366,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-27T02:54:19.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://cdn.thestandnews.com/media/photos/cache/6-01_PBNbD_1200x0.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thestandnews.com%2Fmedia%2Fphotos%2Fcache%2F6-01_PBNbD_1200x0.png&h=7fa96460&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n特首選舉剛結束，警方即落案起訴多名參與佔領行動人士，指他們違反「公眾妨擾罪」。除了公民黨陳淑莊在facebook今早收到警方通知落案，起訴她兩年前參加佔中。羅冠聰稱，佔中三子即戴耀廷、陳健民、朱耀明、在佔運期間擔任咪手的立法會議員邵家臻、社民連黃浩銘等同樣被控。<br />\n<br />\n羅冠聰提到，學聯前常委鍾耀華、張秀賢均接到警方電話，因雨傘運動而被控以「公眾妨擾罪」，今日將到灣仔警署被捕。<br />\n<br />\n羅冠聰稱，預計針對雨傘運動的清算將會繼續，將有更多核心組織者被捕被控。<br />\n<br />\n立場新聞向警方公共關係科查詢，暫時未獲回覆。<br />\n<br />\n邵家臻向港台證實，早上9時於立法會開會期間，收到灣仔警署重案組的電話，電話中的警務人員稱，今日並非要拘捕他，而是要直接起訴他「公眾妨擾罪」及落案，短時間內會上法庭，並提醒他今天要帶1萬元保釋金。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"http://thestandnews.com/politics/%E8%AD%A6%E6%96%B9%E8%90%BD%E6%A1%88%E8%B5%B7%E8%A8%B4%E4%BD%94%E4%B8%AD%E4%B8%89%E5%AD%90-%E5%AD%B8%E8%81%AF%E5%89%8D%E5%B8%B8%E5%A7%94%E7%AD%89%E5%A4%9A%E4%BA%BA-%E6%B6%89-%E5%85%AC%E7%9C%BE%E5%A6%A8%E6%93%BE%E7%BD%AA/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fthestandnews.com%2Fpolitics%2F%25E8%25AD%25A6%25E6%2596%25B9%25E8%2590%25BD%25E6%25A1%2588%25E8%25B5%25B7%25E8%25A8%25B4%25E4%25BD%2594%25E4%25B8%25AD%25E4%25B8%2589%25E5%25AD%2590-%25E5%25AD%25B8%25E8%2581%25AF%25E5%2589%258D%25E5%25B8%25B8%25E5%25A7%2594%25E7%25AD%2589%25E5%25A4%259A%25E4%25BA%25BA-%25E6%25B6%2589-%25E5%2585%25AC%25E7%259C%25BE%25E5%25A6%25A8%25E6%2593%25BE%25E7%25BD%25AA%2F&d=ZU5rKlsKhNp37FgV%2FTwvgp4%2BuNhYgvPKbWZYs3KJomg%3D&h=5d859c0d\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=http%3A%2F%2Fthestandnews.com%2Fpolitics%2F%25E8%25AD%25A6%25E6%2596%25B9%25E8%2590%25BD%25E6%25A1%2588%25E8%25B5%25B7%25E8%25A8%25B4%25E4%25BD%2594%25E4%25B8%25AD%25E4%25B8%2589%25E5%25AD%2590-%25E5%25AD%25B8%25E8%2581%25AF%25E5%2589%258D%25E5%25B8%25B8%25E5%25A7%2594%25E7%25AD%2589%25E5%25A4%259A%25E4%25BA%25BA-%25E6%25B6%2589-%25E5%2585%25AC%25E7%259C%25BE%25E5%25A6%25A8%25E6%2593%25BE%25E7%25BD%25AA%2F&h=2479dba8\" target=\"_blank\">http://thestandnews.com/politics/%E8%AD%A6%E6%96%B9%E8%90%BD%E6%A1%88%E8%B5%B7%E8%A8%B4%E4%BD%94%E4%B8%AD%E4%B8%89%E5%AD%90-%E5%AD%B8%E8%81%AF%E5%89%8D%E5%B8%B8%E5%A7%94%E7%AD%89%E5%A4%9A%E4%BA%BA-%E6%B6%89-%E5%85%AC%E7%9C%BE%E5%A6%A8%E6%93%BE%E7%BD%AA/</a>"},{"pid":"8f3b2f2a49a5f170396aaccfd3d2a50630767123","tid":174613,"uid":83251,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-27T02:55:25.000Z","msg":"白色恐怖"},{"pid":"e9afdf1f1b474ad0e4dcb19c53867ba1759f941c","tid":174613,"uid":83251,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-27T02:55:38.000Z","msg":"來了來了"},{"pid":"bfad9a767bfb44d3de12f391b264cccbd9fd5b79","tid":174613,"uid":61280,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-27T03:14:57.000Z","msg":"<strong><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">要垃&quot;佔中&quot;，點解硬係冇維撚一寶雙輝，同高達賓周，大波Man，陳港文，私煙班仆街份？？</span></span></strong>"},{"pid":"12fe7498efc517a315134c6e5f85fc8ee1995a22","tid":174613,"uid":52651,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-27T03:18:11.000Z","msg":"咁快手?"}]}